      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait sorry that last bit cut off. you were saying something about it being an elaborate ritual? i dont get it. i'm just trying to buy a condo in toronto, not join a cult lol. can you just explain the actual steps of how the money moves from my bank to the escrow and then to the seller?",
